      <p class="subtitle is-size-4"><%= bot.user.username %> can be tweaked and customized in many ways!</p>
      <p>Want to log some events, but not others? And in separate channels? Edit the channel configs!</p>
      <p>Don't want users running a certain command, or even an entire category? You can disable them!</p>
      <p>Want to add custom command responses? That's possible with the addcommand and removecommand commands.</p>
      <p>Want to tweak how message sniping works, add ignored channels, or outright disable it? You can edit the snipe config!</p>
      <p>You can get the best experience configuring <%= bot.user.username %> by using the <a href="/manage/servers" class="has-text-info">dashboard</a>. You'll need permission to manage the server.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

